{"tid":616398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長沙灣狗隻墮樓案　遇害狗隻上周六曾墮海","createTime":"2018-04-04T07:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T07:00:27.000Z","uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a032fe4660c81670aa3f4aea24ee29bcb62c0c9","tid":616398,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"長沙灣狗隻墮樓案　遇害狗隻上周六曾墮海<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=301207&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D301207%26refer%3DShare&d=t8u6QFCGTk6vl1kybkTBg0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=24d2bdc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D301207%26refer%3DShare&h=65bbad58\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=301207&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣發生懷疑虐畜案，一隻狗被發現墮樓死亡，警方拘捕一名男子。<br />\n<br />\n現場是昌華街41號一幢住宅大廈，警員封鎖後巷調查。<br />\n<br />\n早上六時許，警方接獲大廈住客報案，指一隻狗從高處墮下，倒臥在大廈天井，警員到場證實狗隻已經死亡，經調查後在一個單位拘捕一名涉案男子，案件列作虐待動物。<br />\n<br />\n警方消息指，墮樓死去的狗隻上周六被發現在尖沙咀墮海，由水警到場將牠救起，再由愛護動物協會交還狗主。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲記得前幾日佢畀人救起果陣個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主人仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}